 The 4 Step Plan to NOT Suck at Talking to People 
 
 
By Rebel One   95 
 

 
 
 
 
 This is a guest post from my good friend/relationship &amp; dating expert  Lindsay Miller .   
 With Nerd Fitness’s tagline being “level up your life,” I thought it was important for us to level up on the inside as well as the outside.  We can change our outer appearance through strength training and better eating decisions, but oftentimes we forget about leveling up other parts of our lives too.  Believe it or not, some of us nerds struggle with social skills (okay, a lot of us do,